DP.Name: AlignMode
DP.OneState: 1=IRS in STATIONARY ALIGN MODE or ERRECT ATTITUDE MODE

DP.Name: AttitudeMode
DP.OneState: 1=IRS in Errect Attitude or Reversionary Attitude Mode

DP.Name: SetHeading
DP.OneState: 1=Heading Input Entered in Reversionary Attitude or IRS in AIM Attitude Mode
DP.ZeroState: 0=Heading Input Not in Reversionary Attitude or IRS in AIM Attitude Mode

DP.Name: NoInitialization
DP.OneState: 1=Init data not correct or not received

DP.Name: TimetoNav
DP.CodedSet: 0=Transition To Nav;1=0 to 1 Minute;2=1 to 2 Minutes;3= 2 to 3 Minutes;4=3 to 4 Minutes;5=4 to 5 Minutes;6=5 to 6 Minutes;7=greater than 6 Minutes

DP.Name: AlignInMotionMode
DP.OneState: 1=IRU operating in Align In Motion (AIM) Mode

DP.Name: AIMTimetoNav
DP.CodedSet: 0=Transition To Nav;1=0 to 1 Minute;2=1 to 2 Minutes;3= 2 to 3 Minutes;4=3 to 4 Minutes;5=4 to 5 Minutes;6=5 to 6 Minutes;7=6 to 7 Minutes;8=7 to 8 Minutes;9=8 to 9 Minutes;10=9 to 10 Minutes;11=10 to 11 Minutes;12=11 to 12 Minutes;13=12 to 13 Minutes;14=13 to 14 Minutes;15=greater than 14 Minutes
